quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif. Lam. Mim."
  2,2,"That Book has no doubt in it – a guidance for the God-fearing,"
  2,3,"who believe in the unseen, and are steadfast in salah, and spend out of what We have provided them;"
  2,4,"and who believe in what has been revealed to you and what has been revealed before you, and do have faith in the Hereafter."
  2,5,"It is these who are on guidance given by their Lord; and it is just these who are successful."